---
title: Roast Lamb & Smokey Capsicum Yoghurt with Cherry Tomato & Green Bean Salad
description: Savour the comforting flavours of this feast! Tender, juicy lamb pairs beautifully with a smokey, tangy yoghurt sauce, while a bright cherry tomato and green bean salad adds a fresh, vibrant crunch. It’s a deliciously balanced dish that’s both hearty and refreshing—a true crowd-pleaser for any table!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

